imdb.plot outline: Johnny Reid, the two-time JUNO Award winner and acclaimed multi-platinum singer-songwriter celebrates the release of his new album, 'Fire It Up' with new songs, as well as his classics. CMT's Paul McGuire guides the studio audience comprised of Johnny's biggest fans and his infamous tartan army.
